rows.name:
Fuwa-waa! There are so many
ingredients for sale that
I've never seen before, mo!

rows.label: tlk4240008103_msg0002
rows.name:
I can buy the ingredients I
want with my teacher's salary,
mo! I'm so happy, mo!

rows.label: tlk4240008103_msg0003
rows.name:
And I can finally experiment
in a place with a roof over my
head, mo! I'm so glad, mo!

rows.label: tlk4240008103_msg0004
rows.name:
But they said my lessons
were hard to understand...
mo. I'll try my best, mo.
